style.color: function(f) {var type = f.get('type'); if (type == 'breakpoint') {return 'pink';} var name = f._parent.get('Name'); if (typeof name === 'undefined') {return 'red';} if (name.match(/tRNA/)) {return 'gray';} if (name.match(/snoRNA/)) {return 'gray';} if (name.match(/CR[0-9]/)) {return 'gray';} if(name.match(/mir-[0-9]/)) {return 'gray';} return 'goldenrod'; }

tracks.glyph: function(f) {var name = f.get('Name'); if (typeof name === 'undefined') {return 'JBrowse/View/FeatureGlyph/Gene';} if (name.match(/tRNA/)) {return 'JBrowse/View/FeatureGlyph/TRNAGene';} if (name.match(/snoRNA/)) {return 'JBrowse/View/FeatureGlyph/SnoRNAGene';} if (name.match(/CR[0-9]/)) {return 'JBrowse/View/FeatureGlyph/NcRNAGene';} if(name.match(/mir-[0-9]/)) {return 'JBrowse/View/FeatureGlyph/MiRNAGene';} return 'JBrowse/View/FeatureGlyph/WBGene'; }
tracks.label: Genes
